  "text-page-seller-money-header": "A flexible payment system adapted to African artisans",
  "text-artisanat-title1": "Give the best of Africa through crafts",
  "text-artisanat-title2": "Promote the development of local African crafts online",
  "text-artisanat-description1": "Crafts in Africa is a rich form of cultural and economic expression that varies from country to country and region to region. brings back to a long tradition of beauty, handmade and symbolic. Indeed, the traditional African market is a living space where we find products of all kinds. The pharmacopoeia with plants of herbalists, oils and traditional soaps is present.",
  "text-artisanat-description2": "Crafts play an essential economic role in Africa, both locally and nationally. It provides employment and income opportunities for many artisans and communities, promoting economic development and poverty reduction. Thanks to online sales, sAmArA allows artisans to increase exponentially the possibility of national or international sales",

  "text-artisanat-expedition-title": "Shipping of products to sAmArA",
  "text-artisanat-expedition-description": "We have made order processing easier and less expensive with tools such as shipping labels, shipping cost calculations and tracking shipments. Send your buyers packages weighing up to 150 kg throughout Africa and around the world. We can also help you with customs forms.",
  "text-artisanat-deliery-title": "Delivery of products to sAmArA",
  "text-artisanat-deliery-description": "We deliver your products throughout Africa and worldwide. Delivery notes are the record of a transaction for buyers, and are supposed to be included with an order when it is shipped. Receipts are intended to serve as physical records of transactions for sellers. Neither delivery notes nor order receipts are considered invoices for buyers.",
  "text-artisanat-refund-title": "Refund Policy at sAmArA",
  "text-artisanat-refund-description": "Money refunds can only be made if a problem has arisen during the delivery or shipment of the products by sAmArA and if the seller makes a refund request directly to the sAmArA Reclaim Service. Complaints can be made by calling +33748272078",
  "text-om-momo-sub-header": "We process payments with the Mobile Money system, two external payment platforms allowing you to receive orders via Orange Money(OM) and MTN Mobile Money(MoMo). Funds from your sAmArA sales paid by Mobile Money are credited to your OM or MoMo account.",
